name: FOOD to DIE for #6
description: “Kueh Basah” is how we often called a number of traditional Indonesian snacks. It represents many types of cakes with different taste, colors and shapes we usually find in traditional market. These cakes can be said to be timeless, being loved by many generations of people even until today.Therefore, I’d love to raise the topic of “Kueh Basah” with unique interpretation by combining elements of traditional Indonesian clothing and these unique cakes to further enhance the taste of time that “Kueh Basah” brings through.
